title: Photo From Luke Gallows' New Wrestling School, Fans On Iconic Chants, John Cena And Nikki Bella
text:
- Cathy Kelley looks at social media talk on Nikki Bella and John Cena kissing after their SmackDown segment with The Miz and Maryse in this new video from WWE Digital. - WWE has a new poll asking fans which Superstar chant is more iconic - "Goldberg", Daniel Bryan's "Yes", "Stone Cold" Steve Austin "What?", Kurt Angle's "You suck", "Let's go Cena/Cena sucks" or Ric Flair's "Wooo!" As of this writing, 31% went with Bryan while 21% voted for Flair, 17% for Austin, 11% for John Cena and 11% for Bill Goldberg.
- The new Bulletproof Dojo wrestling school in Georgia ran by RAW Tag Team Champion Luke Gallows and former WWE star Joey Mercury is up and running with 20 students in the first class. Gallows tweeted the following photo from the school: Kudos to these 20 young grapplers for traveling from around the country to learn from the incomparable @WWEMercury @bulletproofdojo in GA! pic.twitter.com/EGMQXmy5zy â€” Luke Gallows (@LukeGallowsWWE) March 2, 2017
